	<abstract>
		<para>&THIS.PLATFORM; JAIN SLEE &THIS.RA; Resource Adaptor (<acronym>RA</acronym>) is the JAIN SLEE 1.1 RA for the <acronym>IMS</acronym> Ro Interface, the reference point for Online Charging in <acronym>IMS</acronym> and follows a mechanism where the online client (<acronym>CTF</acronym>) requests resource allocation and reports credit control information to the Online Charging System (<acronym>OCS</acronym>). It is described in <ulink url="http://www.3gpp.org/ftp/Specs/html-info/32260.htm">TS32.260</ulink> and <ulink url="http://www.3gpp.org/ftp/Specs/html-info/32299.htm">TS32.299</ulink> by <acronym>3GPP</acronym>.</para>
		<para>This RA implements the Resource Adaptor Type defined by Mobicents development teams.</para>		
